23 SECTION 5. A NEW SECTION OF KRS CHAPTER 160 IS CREATED TO
24 READ AS FOLLOWS:
25 (1) As used in this section:
26 (a) "Complaint" has the same meaning as in KRS 600.020;
27 (b) "Court-designated worker" has the same meaning as in KRS 600.020; and
